{"id": "1197872754238697523", "channel_id": "1197872754238697523", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "助戰狀態是保存時固定\n還是根據原持有者狀態？\n剛剛借別人的時候 \n對方那邊顯示是更新後的 環拉 魔術帽\n但是進場後又變成  環拉 時針\n可能需要在出借端提示一下助戰設定的效果有沒有同步", "timestamp": "2024-01-19T11:58:40.010000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197872754238697523", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」助戰的配置 會跟進場後不一樣", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1197954900592693358", "channel_id": "1197954900592693358", "type": 0, "author_id": "589115953355423805", "author_name": "magushermes", "author_bot": false, "content": "近期走主線，過到5－7時發現這個事件。\n選擇了「接受挑戰」後出現三個選項，但無論選哪個選項都沒有出現相應的結果？@@", "timestamp": "2024-01-19T17:25:05.227000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1197954901091827822", "filename": "Screenshot_20240120-011713.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 105502, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197954900592693358/1197954901091827822/Screenshot_20240120-011713.jpg?ex=6a00bf71&is=69ff6df1&hm=70091028e50b0f36a2703aa0c01896946710f7d7caec9dcd700d6b62674d6ce5&"}, {"id": "1197954901637091348", "filename": "Screenshot_20240120-012244.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 105294, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197954900592693358/1197954901637091348/Screenshot_20240120-012244.jpg?ex=6a00bf71&is=69ff6df1&hm=de0dd70c737dbfaa430ccfea57c5f9a9f74c56148bb508539633d254b91f3a38&"}, {"id": "1197954901960036502", "filename": "Screenshot_20240120-012252.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 104865, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197954900592693358/1197954901960036502/Screenshot_20240120-012252.jpg?ex=6a00bf71&is=69ff6df1&hm=95af137cad3822466fb6ed17019a948332bb999e4a87e0d7602b25d0bc462dbb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197954900592693358", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」主線5－7的事件沒有作用", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1197896804109389864", "channel_id": "1197896804109389864", "type": 0, "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "author_bot": false, "content": "觸發方式：使莉莉一階段血量達到圖魯深淵號令的斬殺線，同時深淵號令總傷>不滅之花層數>剩餘血量。\n\n具體操作：扔一張深淵號令打掉一階段血量，此時莉莉__意圖替換為覺醒並免疫__，然而深淵號令為穿刺傷害（無視免疫），剩餘傷害打掉不滅之花層數，莉莉__意圖替換為不滅之花__，覺醒被吃掉。\n\n~~||（舊）推測原因為深淵號令的觸手傷害先於免疫應用在莉莉身上，可能因為觸手打出的是多段傷害，不像其他單段傷害能在結算完以後正常扣除溢出部分進入免疫，因此在轉階段時能打掉一部分血。||~~\n（更新）**經過cipher佬的修正，確定是穿刺傷害無視免疫從而導致的意圖覆蓋**\n應該也可應用於尤烏哈希等受到一定攻擊時會替換意圖的敵方身上。\n由於觸發條件過於極端難以復現，當時也沒有錄影，這邊會盡力凹幾場但不保證能提供錄像（）", "timestamp": "2024-01-19T13:34:13.946000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-19T15:51:30.077000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197896804109389864", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」敵方莉莉轉階段時不會覺醒", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1198038854247120917", "channel_id": "1198038854247120917", "type": 0, "author_id": "1084923460326793289", "author_name": "tofu0834", "author_bot": false, "content": "文本敘述為「連續3/4/5個回合使用狂氣爆發則獲得對應計分」，但現在即使規定回合以上每回合皆使用一次狂氣爆發仍無獲得對應計分。\n不確定為文本bug或功能bug。", "timestamp": "2024-01-19T22:58:41.338000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1198038854247120917", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」今（1/20）深潛特別評分「恐怖表演」計分異常", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
