{"id": "1197951057360334888", "channel_id": "1197951057360334888", "type": 0, "author_id": "921442534411100191", "author_name": "07_youer", "author_bot": false, "content": "圖1是我在二算力，打了「防禦」後，先扣除「防禦」的一算力，再因為快樂唱片的效果，再扣除了一算力。因此此時我的算力為0。\n\n可是，這並沒有觸發銀白差分機的效果：（當算力被耗盡時回2點算力，每回合限2次）\n\n圖2是每記錯的話也是一樣的問題，但是卻在我打出「胚胎」後，突然回了兩點算力。\n\n（感覺就像Devis佬說的：＂當你執行動作後，算力=0時獲得2算力，每回合限制兩次＂）\n\n所以這是文字敘述問題還是bug？", "timestamp": "2024-01-19T17:09:48.929000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197951057582620844", "filename": "Screenshot_20240120_001051.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 219055, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197951057360334888/1197951057582620844/Screenshot_20240120_001051.jpg?ex=6a00bbdc&is=69ff6a5c&hm=16c74a04b8fa7d7ffea06e7ec0ed8c949b97a873314ce736ebcedb23590cce41&"}, {"id": "1197951057851072532", "filename": "Screenshot_20240120_002801.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 224233, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197951057360334888/1197951057851072532/Screenshot_20240120_002801.jpg?ex=6a00bbdd&is=69ff6a5d&hm=81d021502c14c6532714aefd8f30ba9c7013d23cdb9885ca300457a40f40f443&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197951057360334888", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」銀白差分機和快樂唱片有衝突。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
